    <div class="legal-page">
      <h1>Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>

      <p>Welcome to https://www.anniewiest.com (the "Site"), owned and operated by the author Annie Wiest. By using this Site, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, do not use the Site.</p>

      <h2>Use of the Site</h2>
      <p>Use the Site only for lawful, non-infringing purposes. Do not damage, hack, or overload it. We may terminate access for violations without notice.</p>

      <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All Site content is protected by copyright and owned by Annie Wiest. View for personal use; do not copy, distribute, or use commercially without permission. Share links only.</p>

      <h2>User-Generated Content (If Applicable)</h2>
      <p>If you post content, you grant us a license to use it on the Site. You are responsible for its legality and non-infringement. We may remove inappropriate content.</p>

      <h2>Privacy</h2>
      <p>See our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for data handling details.</p>

      <h2>Purchases and Payments (If Applicable)</h2>
      <p>Product prices and availability may change. We may refuse orders. Payments go through third-party processors; we do not store full card details.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links and Services</h2>
      <p>Links to external sites are at your own risk. We are not responsible for their content or practices.</p>

      <h2>Disclaimers</h2>
      <p>Site provided "as is" without warranties. Content may have errors; use at your own risk. No guarantees of availability or security from viruses.</p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>We are not liable for any damages from Site use. Liability limited to amounts paid (if any), where permitted by law.</p>

      <h2>Indemnification</h2>
      <p>You agree to indemnify us against claims from your Site use or violations.</p>

      <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>Updates posted here. Continued use means acceptance.</p>

      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms are governed by international laws, without regard to conflict laws. Disputes subject to courts there.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Annie Wiest<br />Email: info@anniewiest.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
